Important Interview Point

This condition is the KEY:

if(!set.contains(num - 1))

Without this:

Time Complexity becomes worse

because sequences are recalculated repeatedly.

Easy Memory Trick

Think:

START ONLY FROM THE SMALLEST NUMBER

How to know smallest?

num - 1 should not exist

Then keep moving forward.
